{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01UDk7o9Av7eBiUve7Pu6uKH","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The demo namespace has no Ingress resources (the earlier `kubectl -n demo get ingress -o yaml` returned an empty list). There's no Service for the demo-app either. Let me check the ingress-nginx namespace more carefully - specifically the webhook configuration and any ClusterRole/RBAC.\n\nKey findings so far:\n1. **Controller version**: v1.14.1 (image: `registry.k8s.io/ingress-nginx/controller:v1.14.1@sha256:...`)\n2. **Controller args** (live, not just the applied config):\n   - `--election-id=ingress-nginx-leader`\n   - `--controller-class=k8s.io/ingress-nginx`\n   - `--ingress-class=nginx`\n   - `--configmap=$(POD_NAMESPACE)/ingress-nginx-controller`\n   - `--validating-webhook=:8443`\n   - `--validating-webhook-certificate=/usr/local/certificates/cert`\n   - `--validating-webhook-key=/usr/local/certificates/key`\n   - `--watch-ingress-without-class=true` (in the applied config)\n   - `--publish-status-address=localhost`\n\nThere's a conflict with `--watch-ingress-without-class` where the applied config sets it to true but the live deployment also has false appended, which overrides it since the last value wins. The ConfigMap has no custom settings, there are no Ingress resources defined in the demo namespace, and the demo app is just a busybox httpd on port 5678 without any Service or Ingress routing. The `--publish-status-address=localhost` is also non-standard configuration.\n\nI'm noticing several other unusual settings: the termination grace period is set to zero which is quite aggressive, the controller has tolerations to run on control-plane nodes, and the LoadBalancer Service is pending without an external IP. I should look into the webhook configuration and IngressClass resources to get a fuller picture of what's happening here.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1269,"cache_read_input_tokens":36660,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1269},"output_tokens":20,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"669e364a-6af2-4d89-b7ef-d24af1caf6a6","uuid":"bf290712-5632-4947-93b5-2bfc6f359a27","request_id":"req_011CcL9Unm3CK8FszQ7TZbft"}
